The paper discusses the detection problem in LS-MIMO systems, which is a subfield of wireless communication and signal processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
